          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-4 col-12-medium">
              <section class="first">
                <i class="icon solid featured fa-puzzle-piece"></i>
                <header>
                  <h2>Type-Safe Steps</h2>
                </header>
                <p>Generic steps catch payload mismatches at compile time. Every step declares its input, output, and config through a single StepDef.</p>
              </section>
            </div>
            <div class="col-4 col-12-medium">
              <section class="middle">
                <i class="icon solid featured alt fa-bolt"></i>
                <header>
                  <h2>Zero-Alloc Hot Path</h2>
                </header>
                <p>Pre-allocated buffers and zero-copy passing. Init() allocates, Process() is allocation-free. Built for 120fps camera pipelines, not batch ETL.</p>
              </section>
            </div>
            <div class="col-4 col-12-medium">
              <section class="last">
                <i class="icon solid featured alt2 fa-chart-bar"></i>
                <header>
                  <h2>Built-In Observability</h2>
                </header>
                <p>Every step tracks latency automatically. Topic pub/sub powers multi-engine architectures. Studio shows live pipeline graphs with per-step timing.</p>
              </section>
            </div>
